  <div class="ex-details">
    <h2>Comprehensive Women's Health</h2>
    <p>Our gynecologists are experts in managing a full spectrum of conditions &mdash; from PCOS and endometriosis to fibroids, menstrual disorders, and gynecological cancers. Every treatment plan is personalised based on your age, lifestyle, and long-term wellbeing.</p>
    <p>We believe that great gynaecology care is as much about listening as it is about treating. Private consultation suites, discreet scheduling, and a compassionate all-women nursing team create a space where you can speak freely about anything.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>PCOS / PCOD management</li>
      <li>Endometriosis treatment</li>
      <li>Fibroid surgery</li>
      <li>Menstrual disorder care</li>
      <li>Urogynaecology</li>
      <li>Cervical cancer screening</li>
      <li>HPV vaccination</li>
      <li>Adolescent gynaecology</li>
    </ul>
